OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775239864
OL,3,C'New IRA' admits responsibility for
OL,4,Cattempted police station bomb attack
OL,6,FThe New IRA has claimed responsibility
OL,7,Ffor an attempted proxy bomb attack
OL,8,Ftargeting a Northern Ireland police
OL,9,Fstation earlier this week.
OL,11,FA pizza delivery driver was forced at
OL,12,Fgunpoint to take the bomb to the
OL,13,Fpolice station. He was able to alert
OL,14,Fthose in the station to the deadly
OL,15,Fdevice.
OL,17,FThe device was described as 'crude and
OL,18,Fviable'. PSNI chief constable said
OL,19,F'cowards' were behind the attack and
OL,20,Fit was a reminder of the past.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
