OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775239864
OL,3,C'New IRA' admits responsibility for
OL,4,Cattempted police station bomb attack
OL,6,FMr Boutcher said the incident is
OL,7,F"likely to have been a sad attempt to
OL,8,Fappear relevant ahead of planned
OL,9,Fdissident Republican parades over
OL,10,FEaster".
OL,12,FThe incident was condemned by
OL,13,Fpolitical leaders across Northern
OL,14,FIreland.
OL,16,FMr Boutcher told the policing board on
OL,17,FThursday that investigation into the
OL,18,Fattack is ongoing but "there is little
OL,19,Fdoubt that dissident Republicans were
OL,20,Fresponsible".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@GO]zD@WOU|D@LO]
