OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775239864
OL,3,C'New IRA' admits responsibility for
OL,4,Cattempted police station bomb attack
OL,6,F"I want to pay particular tribute to
OL,7,Fthe courageous delivery driver who
OL,8,Falerted officers to the threat, and
OL,9,Fask that people consider the contrast
OL,10,Fbetween the cowards that perpetrated
OL,11,Fthis and that delivery driver and all
OL,12,Fthose countless people in our society
OL,13,Fwho repeatedly stand up against such
OL,14,Funsupported acts of terrorism or acts
OL,15,Fof intimidation.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
