OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1775239864
OL,3,C'New IRA' admits responsibility for
OL,4,Cattempted police station bomb attack
OL,6,F"There is no place in a democratic
OL,7,Fsociety for such criminals and I
OL,8,Fappeal to anyone with any information
OL,9,Fwhatsoever to come forward and tell us
OL,10,Fwhat they know, tell us who was
OL,11,Finvolved before these idiots cause
OL,12,Fsome harm.
OL,14,F"They do not deserve anyone's
OL,15,Fprotection or support."
